race.comment: HOLLYWOOD MISS (1) chased the lead early from the inside and boxed on well to finish third, beaten 4.5 lengths (27.86) at this track in a Grade 5 over 488m. Goes very well from this draw with two wins and two minor placings from five starts. Deserves serious consideration. INCREDIBLE KING (2) has a strong record here with two wins and two placings from six starts. Missed the frame latest (30.09) when sixth over 509m at Northam in a OPEN. Among the main chances. SEEK TO PLAN (3) placed last time (27.77) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten 2.75 lengths. Already a winner from this draw. Can hit the frame with the right run. MAGIC ENTRY (6) is not to be discarded.
